    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And Shobal, the father of Kirjathjearim had sons,.... Which shows that Kirjathjearim is not the name of a man, or of any of Shobal's sons, who are next mentioned, but of a place of which he was prince: the first is ",
        "children": []
